<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Exercise 14.1 - Display and Visibility</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>

  <section class="p-4">
    <h2>Exercise 14.1: Responsive Display Utilities</h2>
    <div class="d-none d-md-block bg-primary text-white p-3 mb-3">
      This content is hidden on xs and sm, visible as block on md and lg.
    </div>
    <div class="d-none d-lg-flex bg-success text-white p-3">
      This content is hidden below lg and displayed as flex on lg and larger.
    </div>
  </section>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
